{"tid":2363305,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"疫苗令你興奮 - 高慧然","createTime":"2021-01-12T06:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T06:25:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ed15188882bd861e6322dd5fb3ef6119b3aa91b9","tid":2363305,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T06:03:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210112/SA3ZK2MQ65D2TCSPVDZB7MK2NU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210112%2FSA3ZK2MQ65D2TCSPVDZB7MK2NU%2F&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJuW1VrQWH3Jev0gRtxLi1IiE%3D&h=3985e151\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210112%2FSA3ZK2MQ65D2TCSPVDZB7MK2NU%2F&h=86024a19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210112/SA3ZK2MQ65D2TCSPVDZB7MK2NU/</a><br />\n<br />\n疫苗令你興奮 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rH5bPxir_jAsh8z_KrJFwOT3jjg=/1118x742/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IUA2ULQKMNF4XAY56B7ATJIFSM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrH5bPxir_jAsh8z_KrJFwOT3jjg%3D%2F1118x742%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIUA2ULQKMNF4XAY56B7ATJIFSM.png&h=f6b22c33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港再出發fb截圖<br />\n<br />\n盧寵茂打完中國製疫苗後，有異於一般人的反應：舒服又興奮。<br />\n<br />\n這種感覺，通常很難同一時間出現。人類感覺舒服，一般隨之而來的是放鬆、平和、平靜。「又舒服又興奮」這種詭異的狀態，當然也會發生在正常人類身上，比如打飛機的時候。<br />\n<br />\n中國製疫苗有另類功能，只有試過的人才知道。唔知私煙當時是甚麼感覺？是走得很舒服，還是因為太興奮，所以走了？<br />\n<br />\n我有個醫生朋友，在加拿大的醫院任職胸肺科顧問醫生，屬第一批必須打疫苗的人。打之前，他考慮了很久，主要原因是疫苗問世時間太短，沒做過廣泛的、長時間的測試。某些副作用現階段尚未有機會得知。但是，他考慮的結果還是要打疫苗，因為他並無選擇。打完之後，他傳訊息給我：「Got my vaccine, still alive, still doing ok.」我完全感受得到他的忐忑與不安。這是一個醫生的正常反應，他受過醫學及科學的訓練，知道短時間問世、測試時間不足夠的疫苗，並不太值得信賴。正因為是醫生，所以不會盲目興奮。當然，加拿大政府購入的疫苗沒有一支是中國製造，所以，它缺乏中國疫苗的另類功能。<br />\n<br />\n有說權力是春藥，直接獲得權力固然令權力愛好者興奮，接近權力，或者做了某件事，深信向權力中心邁進了一大步，也同樣有春藥般的效果，令權力愛好者又舒服又興奮。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook：kowaiyin.yoyoko"},{"pid":"d3603ecc5d25960713042654e2cbf68a068562f6","tid":2363305,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T06:19:29.000Z","msg":"「又舒服又興奮」這種詭異的狀態，當然也會發生在正常人類身上，比如打飛機的時候。"},{"pid":"0357500b819abc3017f55f1d27ede3b3cb8d0505","tid":2363305,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d3603ecc5d25960713042654e2cbf68a068562f6","tid":2363305,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T06:19:29.000Z","msg":"「又舒服又興奮」這種詭異的狀態，當然也會發生在正常人類身上，比如打飛機的時候。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T06:25:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}